# Iconography

Which icon set the product uses, sizing conventions, accessibility rules.

## Icon library

- **Library:** {{Lucide_/_Heroicons_/_Phosphor_/_custom}}
- **Import path:** {{lucide-react_/_...}}
- **Default size:** {{16px_/_20px_/_24px}}

## Sizing scale

| Token | Size | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `--icon-xs` | {{12px}} | inline text-badges |
| `--icon-sm` | {{16px}} | default inline |
| `--icon-md` | {{20px}} | buttons, input affordances |
| `--icon-lg` | {{24px}} | prominent actions |
| `--icon-xl` | {{32px+}} | hero / empty-state |

## Rules

- Icon-only buttons must have `aria-label`
- Decorative icons get `aria-hidden="true"`
- Color from semantic token (`--color-text-primary` etc.), never hard-coded
- Icon + text pairings: icon leads for actions (`[icon] Save`), text leads for metadata (`Created: [icon]`)

